msgid "CMAKE_INSTALL_DEFAULT_COMPONENT_NAME-project-name-placeholder"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/dev/CMAKE_INSTALL_DEFAULT_COMPONENT_NAME-project-name-placeholder.rst:4
msgid ""
":variable:`CMAKE_INSTALL_DEFAULT_COMPONENT_NAME` gained support for a "
"special ``<PROJECT_NAME>`` placeholder value.   It tells each :command:"
"`install` invocation to take a default component name from the current :"
"variable:`PROJECT_NAME` variable value."
msgstr ""
